WorldStage Newsonline– May & Baker Nigeria Plc on Monday announced the retirement of Mr. Nnamdi Nathan Okafor as Director and Managing Director of the Company with effect from 31st December 2020 and the appointment of Mr. Patrick O. Ajah as an Executive Director of the Company with effect from 31st December, 2020 and Managing Director of the Company with effect from 1st January, 2021. In a notice filed at the Nigerian Stock Exchange, the company said the retirement was accepted at the Board Meeting held on Thursday,26th November, 2020 at the Muson Centre, Onikan, Lagos. Patrick Ajah holds a Bachelor of Pharmacy degree from the University of Ibadan, 1994 and also has a MBA (Marketing) from Obafemi Awolowo University, Ile-Ife – 2005. He is a passionate and visionary leader with over two decades of progressive experience and responsibility in a variety of business environments.